Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had joined some other circle, I would have surely spent quite a different two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:03.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まったく別の　２年間を送っていただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何より　小津と出会ってしまったのは　最大の敗因である
